WEBVTT

00:03:56.669 --> 00:04:01.244
I'm not saying that I shouldn't pay.

00:04:01.244 --> 00:04:04.982
All I'm asking is for forgiveness.

00:04:04.982 --> 00:04:11.921
Gotta have hope I'll be free someday.

00:04:16.731 --> 00:04:22.605
Is there a place for me

00:04:22.605 --> 00:04:26.901
in the world out there?

00:04:26.901 --> 00:04:33.800
Will they ever know or care
that I'm chained?